channel.description:
to mention for the client to work with your source you gotta go to client.java and search (555) then you should see something like this [code] aClass30_Sub2_Sub2_847.method398(255); aClass30_Sub2_Sub2_847.method399(555); [/code] switch the 555 to 317 then save compile and it should work then Heres the links for client and source: Source is 0.61mb link: http://uppit.com/v/XHKZ6ZZ6 Client Kinda big Its 21.04mb link: http://uppit.com/v/2GQ52T9Y it has almost full Duel Arena credits 100% Me for it has Full bounty hunter credits 100% owner fritz has custom interfaces has 100% clanchat fully working equipment tab Credits 50% shkic 50% CoonHunter nice pvp area Perfect Claws with special Perfect Pvp armour nice pk point exchange good pest control shitty barrows same old assualt home is edge with shops and objects all around for bounty hunter you go to edgeville dungeon full lunar, ancients, and normal magic almost perfect vengeance well heres a few pictures Vengeances! [img]http://i406.photobucket.com/albums/pp146/babykid13/veng-1.jpg[/img] Pvp! [img]http://i406.photobucket.com/albums/pp146/babykid13/pvp.jpg[/img] Pvp Shop! [img]http://i406.photobucket.com/albums/pp146/babykid13/pvpshop.jpg[/img] Bounty Hunter! [img]http://i406.photobucket.com/albums/pp146/babykid13/bh.jpg[/img] Dragon Claws! [img]http://i406.photobucket.com/albums/pp146/babykid13/dclaws.jpg[/img] Dueling and Stacking! [img]http://i406.photobucket.com/albums/pp146/babykid13/stacking.jpg[/img] i didnt really add many npcs so pretty much the same npcs as delta besides shops well that about covers it hope you like my last release please comment let me know what you think :) Bye :D Oh one last picture i wanted to post was my welcome screen interface and here it is [IMG]http://i406.photobucket.com/albums/pp146/babykid13/welcome.jpg[/img]
[size=24pt]Download = rep++ Thanks!!! ;D[/size]
